description: Try our easy to follow Cherry Lamingtons recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Cherry Lamingtons Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Using 2 forks, and working quickly, dip each ice-cream block into chocolate to coat and sprinkle with coconut. Return to freezer until ready to serve. Serve with remaining cherry sauce.
